{"tid":1869090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"男童福建拔喉　入境送院命危","createTime":"2020-02-08T03:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T03:34:56.000Z","uid":249945,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5d9df91d1e9089ae89915f30f28de3b9e2bc0368","tid":1869090,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:33:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200208/B2TU2TXJHV7C5ZLP7JIGLMF774\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200208%2FB2TU2TXJHV7C5ZLP7JIGLMF774&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=877c367c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200208%2FB2TU2TXJHV7C5ZLP7JIGLMF774&h=5aaee5c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200208/B2TU2TXJHV7C5ZLP7JIGLMF774</a><br />\n<br />\n【前線醫護有料報？MI報料專線：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3aNNpcK】\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3aNNpcK%E3%80%91&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=21f78154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3aNNpcK】</a><br />\n<br />\n政府前日（5日）宣佈明日（8日）凌晨起，經由內地來港人士需要強制接受檢疫14天，強制檢疫措施實施前，大量人衝關來港。今早近八時，一名年約8歲的男童過關後，隨即表示身體不適，並在關口召救護車送院治理。據悉，男童現時情況危殆，仍需等候新型冠狀病毒測試報告。<br />\n<br />\n負責接載男童的救護員均穿上全套保護裝備，為男童戴上氧氣罩，男童由兩名男子陪同上救護車，然後送往屯門醫院治理。消息指，男童原本在福建某醫院接受肺炎相關診治，及需插喉治療。疑有人得悉本港即將實施強制檢疫，便決定安排男童「拔喉」離院、「衝關」來港。據了解，男童現時在屯門醫院插喉接受治療，在負壓病房留醫，肺部X光片顯示有重肺炎跡象。據悉，男童除了患上嚴重肺炎，亦有先天性心臟病。<br />\n<br />\n閱讀更多文章：<br />\n【武漢肺炎】《刺針》刊金銀潭病例研究：逾兩成病人入ICU、一成死亡；男長者慢性病患更易受感染。<br />\n<a href=\"https://medicalinspire.com/web/posts/47474\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedicalinspire.com%2Fweb%2Fposts%2F47474&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=21fd270d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medicalinspire.com/web/posts/47474</a><br />\n<br />\n#MedicalInspire #衝關 #武漢肺炎 #口罩 #醫思維<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------<br />